#: ../../source/moduli/io_utils/load-csv.md:19
msgid ""
"`load_csv` carica un file CSV in un `DataFrame` pandas con controlli espliciti su rinomina "
"colonne, colonne richieste e valori mancanti."
msgstr ""
"`load_csv` loads a CSV file into a pandas `DataFrame` with explicit checks for column renaming, "
"required columns, and missing values."

